{"id": 1910, "title": "Ticket #1910: Error case in the fix for #1490", "description": "<blockquote>\nIn the fix for ticket <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=1490\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('1490'); return false;\" title=\"condor_hold + condor_rm of DAG goofs things up\">#1490</a></span>, there is a problem: if two jobs refer to <strong>each other</strong> in their <span class=\"wiki\"><a class=\"missing\" href=\"wiki?p=OtherJobRemoveRequirements\" title=\"Other Job Remove Requirements\">OtherJobRemoveRequirements</a></span> expressions, removing one of them puts the schedd into an infinite loop.  I've looked into this some, and for 7.5.6, at least, I'm going to leave thing as-is, because fixing it (or at least figuring out how to fix it) is pretty complicated, and it's a case that will never happen unless the user monkeys around with the <span class=\"wiki\"><a class=\"missing\" href=\"wiki?p=OtherJobRemoveRequirements\" title=\"Other Job Remove Requirements\">OtherJobRemoveRequirements</a></span> expressions themselves.</blockquote>", "remarks": "<blockquote>\n</blockquote>", "derived_tickets": "", "attachments": "<html><head></head><body></body></html>", "check_ins": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2011-Feb-09 18:43</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/51e3dd8796829cf832eca84d3ee176279f8b4415\">[25856]</a></span>: Documented the problem with cycles in <span class=\"wiki\"><a class=\"missing\" href=\"wiki?p=OtherJobRemoveRequirements\" title=\"Other Job Remove Requirements\">OtherJobRemoveRequirements</a></span> expressions (gittrac <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"new\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=1910\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('1910'); return false;\" title=\"Error case in the fix for #1490\">#1910</a></span>); also documented the <span class=\"wiki\"><a class=\"missing\" href=\"wiki?p=OtherJobRemoveRequirements\" title=\"Other Job Remove Requirements\">OtherJobRemoveRequirements</a></span> attribute in the condor_submit man page.  (By Kent Wenger )</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>", "type": "defect", "last_change": "2012-Oct-17 12:41", "status": "new", "created": "2011-Feb-09 16:54", "fixed_version": "2011-Feb-09 16:54", "broken_version": "v070506", "priority": "2", "subsystem": "Daemons", "assigned_to": "", "derived_from": "#1490", "creator": "wenger", "rust": "", "customer_group": "other", "visibility": "public", "notify": "wenger@cs.wisc.edu, psilord@cs.wisc.edu, tannenba@cs.wisc.edu", "due_date": ""}